{"tid":1398374,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[借朋友ac] [多圖] 暢遊奧海城攻略","createTime":"2019-08-02T18:47:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T07:02:50.000Z","uid":69395,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"133ef6e3286fc2b378ed43f5c1b757dcefc5fb15","tid":1398374,"uid":69395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:47:39.000Z","msg":"[借朋友ac post]<br />\n(其實小弟絕對唔推薦大家入奧海城，原因請見：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1397668/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1397668/page/1</a><br />\n如果真係入咗去，希望呢份簡介可以幫到你。)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">TLDR: 如非必要唔好入奧海城，於奧運附近 (尤其二/三期) 離開時，千萬不要向南走。請往大角咀/旺角/南昌方向離去。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n聽講聽日會有人嚟大角咀奧運旺角一日遊，作為二十年街坊，當然要一盡地主之誼。今次就等小弟同大家介紹一下區內大商場 &mdash; 奧海城，等大家聽日唔會咁易盪失路。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n奧海城有一二三期，三個商場靠天橋同奧運站互通。以下我將會簡單介紹每個商場嘅主要出入口，方便大家辨認。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>奧海城三期：</strong><br />\n三期最近旺角，有三個主要出入口：<br />\n1. 天橋出亞皆老街<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z0RSbVG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ0RSbVG.jpg&h=61e51002&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n喺三期嘅盡頭 (鴻福堂對出)，直出亞皆老街去旺角街市/朗豪坊，亦可以沿塘尾道北行入大角咀或沿渡船街南行往油麻地。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9jnFkRj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9jnFkRj.jpg&h=af84f5ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(上圖：往旺角街市方向落橋。)<br />\n2. 天橋入奧海城二期 <br />\n喺三期嘅另一個盡頭 (george coffee 同 帝峯皇殿入口/das gute 中間) (二期部分會講多少少點走法)<br />\n3. 地面出口往海富苑<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YFSuedK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYFSuedK.jpg&h=47ad7919&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n喺往二期天橋附近 (穿過george coffee，落美心香港地對出扶手電梯)，但個人覺得條路線麻麻，因為只可以穿櫻桃街公園上天橋往登打士街或果欄 (自己睇路))。直接向南行 (富榮、HKCC) 好易畀狗咬 (下面會講)。<br />\n(4. 地面出口往海富苑)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tkEwsB2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtkEwsB2.jpg&h=1a6c2bf1&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q4JEBvq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq4JEBvq.jpg&h=e15977a2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n(較隱蔽，唔係街坊未必知點行) 喺大眾書局隔離落扶手電梯，然後直出。不建議，原因同出口3一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>奧海城二期： </strong><br />\n事實上係有好撚多個出口，而主要出入口有三個：<br />\n1. 天橋往奧海城三期 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w0ixb4J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw0ixb4J.jpg&h=32ed3eeb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n入口喺uniqlo同starbucks嗰邊 (pret a manger 隔離)，之後點走請睇返上面。<br />\n2. 奧運站 (D出口)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gpRZByQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgpRZByQ.jpg&h=13c8fdcd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n好易搵到，喺正無印上面。A及E出口可通奧海城一期，B及C出口可通大角咀。<br />\n3. 天橋往柏景灣巴士總站及海富商場<br />\n喺UG (六福對出) 沿長走廊向豐澤/UCC/戲院方向直行至盡頭，<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Yj05tm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Yj05tm.jpg&h=136da8e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去到利寶閣轉左，你會見到天橋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8MQvJf6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8MQvJf6.jpg&h=639aa4e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n穿過天橋，你會見到分岔路，左邊扶手電梯落巴士總站，右邊上斜後轉左直行可經天橋入海富商場<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sr9DSbo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSr9DSbo.jpg&h=1210d3d7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n唔知到時重有冇巴士 (記唔記得7/7夜晚 (雖然係十一點幾) 柏景灣巴士總站冇曬車? 同埋對出海泓道都未必有車搭 (因封路/可能有佔路))。另外去到海富都冇咩路走，向南走好易畀狗咬，都係得返向東行經櫻桃街公園上登打士街天橋，或者出返旺角。請自行判斷。<br />\n(4. 地面大電視出口)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P66Scf1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP66Scf1.jpg&h=93af71c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(uniqlo嗰邊，G/F pandora隔離) 出到去一係搭的士，一係過馬路去返大角咀 (起點附近位置，富多來/新九龍嗰頭) 或櫻桃街公園。巴士好少停呢個位，小巴就算經過，大部分都係帶到你去附近位置 (e.g. 維港灣、匯豐中心)。請自行判斷。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>奧海城一期：</strong><br />\n戴返頭盔先，我冇咁熟呢邊，請大家不要盡信，建議先fact check。<br />\n1. 奧運站 (A及E出口)<br />\nA出口: 一期7/11左邊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AeekmcK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAeekmcK.jpg&h=6cd02d6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nE出口:  一期7/11右邊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tx0fUx9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTx0fUx9.jpg&h=a962515f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n上圖：一出E出口會見到嘅嘢<br />\n前面可搭電梯落地面出口 (出口3)<br />\n2. 天橋直出海輝道海帆道交界 (較隱蔽)<br />\n入到一期往吉野家及大家樂方向行，見到mos cafe轉左，你會見到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VSETGif.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVSETGif.jpg&h=c4b28310&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n直行轉右 (圍住mos cafe咁行)，你會見到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NyGCoyJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNyGCoyJ.jpg&h=2d1db502&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開門，一路沿條橋行，去到政府部門分岔路轉左落橋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YuWCozc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYuWCozc.jpg&h=67743211&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G00ccsy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG00ccsy.jpg&h=eb4d0823&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n落橋後<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0rbVUGf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0rbVUGf.jpg&h=83e856ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住一路向前行理論上會去到南昌<br />\n3. 地面出口<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XGYxcmy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXGYxcmy.jpg&h=40c27690&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喺7/11對出落咗扶手電梯後：<br />\n轉左可出大門，但直行會出海皮，不建議；可出大門後轉右沿海帆道往北行，會join返出口2。<br />\n轉右可經一堆地產鋪入巴士總站。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>慎防狗咬，請留意並避免前往/經過以下地點：</strong><br />\n1. 新油麻地狗屋 (exactly喺海富同富榮南面!!!!!!)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/05OtvgM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F05OtvgM.png&h=e4626130&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2. 西九龍狗竇 (港灣豪庭隔離)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5r7ueJH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5r7ueJH.png&h=b430e11f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n呢個只係小弟作為街坊嘅一啲分享，有錯請不吝指正。衷心希望大家到時用唔著呢份攻略。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後祝大家旅途愉快，平安歸來!!!!"},{"pid":"45ccd1fbdd35dea607e840eed63a81f89743ada7","tid":1398374,"uid":245059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:53:05.000Z","msg":"話時話要走嗰陣行君匯港嗰邊嗰個出口走有冇得諗"},{"pid":"4d22c731cc3a6a58cd78e5486d86c347a51866ea","tid":1398374,"uid":169264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"45ccd1fbdd35dea607e840eed63a81f89743ada7","tid":1398374,"uid":245059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:53:05.000Z","msg":"話時話要走嗰陣行君匯港嗰邊嗰個出口走有冇得諗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T19:00:37.000Z","msg":"如果行君匯港，即係向大角咀方向行。好似係奧運站A/B出口（匯豐中心個邊）。但行到落大角咀 ，小心唔好行到去港灣豪庭（有狗竇）盡量向塘尾道方向走。"},{"pid":"64a349379215efcfc3a934cd5b5b44e4c3bf75ad","tid":1398374,"uid":69395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d22c731cc3a6a58cd78e5486d86c347a51866ea","tid":1398374,"uid":169264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"45ccd1fbdd35dea607e840eed63a81f89743ada7","tid":1398374,"uid":245059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:53:05.000Z","msg":"話時話要走嗰陣行君匯港嗰邊嗰個出口走有冇得諗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T19:00:37.000Z","msg":"如果行君匯港，即係向大角咀方向行。好似係奧運站A/B出口（匯豐中心個邊）。但行到落大角咀 ，小心唔好行到去港灣豪庭（有狗竇）盡量向塘尾道方向走。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T19:07:54.000Z","msg":"係，我冇提到呢part，因為自己都唔係太熟<br />\n主要係經B/C出口經匯豐平台上天橋去君匯港，但出口會近港灣，所以要小心"},{"pid":"560c883bbf2ed5f86a5a4c7551f47df472461339","tid":1398374,"uid":245059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T19:12:22.000Z","msg":"好 幫推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b2a8656ef584ba9d8c1b0516817c56128843e8","tid":1398374,"uid":69395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T19:16:55.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"